Package: eradio
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: A minimalist radio player for audio streaming created for Elementary OS.
 eRadio (e stands for Elementary) is a simple desktop application designed for Elementary OS. Created with Granite Framework and vala language. User is able to create a list of stations by providing their streaming url and then listen to them.
